b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1061,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Version 1.16.2 Update [Update]","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1580959800\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><\/div><div>The following issue was also fixed in the data update applied at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1580959800\\"><\/span>.<br>\\u30fbAdded text saying &quot;<u><strong>The items and amounts received are chosen at random.<\/strong><\/u>&quot; in the Quest Details screen&#39;s drop rewards and survival bonus sections.<br>Note: This information was already present in the Survival Bonus part of the Quest section in the Help menu.<\/div><div><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1580958000\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>An automatic update to version 1.16.2 was applied at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1580958000\\"><\/span>. Here are some more details about its contents.<br><br>\\u30fbFixed an issue where the effects of certain abilities where incorrectly applied multiple times to enemies afflicted with a defense debuff.<br>\\u30fbFixed an issue where certain adventurers&#39; skill gauges didn&#39;t refill automatically after reviving.<br>\\u30fbFixed an issue where Gala Elisanne&#39;s Celestial Ascent skill gauge didn&#39;t decrease automatically even while not under the effects of Divine Revelation and while the skill gauge wasn&#39;t full.<br>\\u30fbFixed an issue where Summer Verica&#39;s Moment of Passion skill gauge didn&#39;t refill automatically until after using her Everlasting Summer skill once.<br>\\u30fbFixed an issue where the Mentor Bonus text in the Quest Details screens of the Advanced Dragon Trials in Standard and Expert difficulties was displayed in Japanese regardless of the game&#39;s language settings.<br><br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send the following items to all players who started playing before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1580958000\\"><\/span>.<br><br>\\u30fbTenfold summon voucher x1<br><br>These items can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>Update 1.16.2, which fixes issues with certain abilities&#39; effects being applied multiple times when attacking an enemy afflicted with a defense debuff, and with certain adventurers&#39; skill gauges not refilling correctly after reviving, was released at approximately <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1580871600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>An automatic update will occur at approximately <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1580958000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Notes<\/div><div>It may take some time for the update information to be reflected in the store.<\/div><div>You may not be able to perform the update if your device&#39;s data cache is full.<\/div><div>If you are unable to perform the update, please restart your device, wait a few minutes, and try to download it from the store once more.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1580872200,"prev_article_id":"1050","next_article_id":"1054","image_path":"","update_time":1580959868}}}'